com.ostrichemulators.semtool.ui.components.api

Interface IPlaySheet

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppDupeHeatMapSheet, BrowserPlaySheet2, ChartItPlaySheet, ColumnChartPlaySheet, ConsistencyPlaySheet, CONUSMapPlaySheet, CountyHeatMapPlaySheet, DendrogramPlaySheet, DupeHeatMapSheet, GraphPlaySheet, GridPlaySheet, GridRAWPlaySheet, GridScatterSheet, HeatMapPlaySheet, ImageExportingPlaySheet, LoadingPlaySheetBase, NodeLoadingPlaySheet, OCONUSMapPlaySheet, ParallelCoordinatesPlaySheet, PieChartPlaySheet, PlaySheetCentralComponent, PropertyEditorPlaySheet, RelationshipLoadingPlaySheet, SankeyPlaySheet, TreeGraphPlaySheet, USHeatMapPlaySheet, WorldHeatMapPlaySheet

    public interface IPlaySheet
    This interface class is used to define the basic functionality for all play sheet classes. A play sheet is loosely defined as any class that displays data on the the main PlayPane Desktop. This serves as the primary interface for all of the play sheets.

    The functions associated with this interface revolve around specifying the data to display and creating the visualization.

    Version:
    $Revision: 1.0 $
    Author:
    karverma
